### **2. 22_APIFlowObserver**  
**Description:**  
A tool to monitor a set of endpoints and display latency and status in a single report.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APIFlowObserver - Multi-Endpoint Latency Tracker

APIFlowObserver gives fast, clear insight into the responsiveness and uptime of any set of HTTP services.

## Features
- Measures latency + logs HTTP code  
- Supports bulk URL checks  
- Optional file export  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_APIFlowObserver.git
cd 22_APIFlowObserver
python monitor.py
